name: 1. Research/science
description: Inherent risk in unknown cutting edge research or science

name: 2. Financial
description: Funding not fully confirmed or at risk of being cut

name: 3. Partnership
description: Risk that partners won’t be able to deliver a key piece on time

name: 4. Internal resources
description: Risk that key staff, infrastructure or equipment not available at time needed

name: 5. Weather
description: For example,  drought or heavy rain affecting field trials

name: 6. External environment (political, economic, legal, market)
description: E.g. risk of non-delivery due to conflict, economic/market changes
